{"id":505354,"date":[{"year":1970,"month":9,"day":30}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激","column":"庆祝中华人民共和国成立二十一周年,国庆献诗","genre":"","count":"174","ytitle":"","mtitle":"毛主席挥笔天下红","ftitle":"","authors":["仲茂兴"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民造纸厂　仲茂兴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造纸机旁春意浓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江河千里如长龙；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接国庆劲头足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"条条江河流向东。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白纸滚滚思潮动——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福不忘旧时痛:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸写过卖儿契，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主债券逼我穷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今毛主席挥巨笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四卷红书唤工农。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我跟党要跟一辈子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗志好比不老松。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接四届人大的召开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的胜利靠群众。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我造新纸献给党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席挥笔天下红。"}]}